    'svc.oto.name':'Otoplasty','svc.oto.desc':'Correction of prominent ears for a natural result and restored confidence. Quick procedure with discreet scars behind the ear.','svc.oto.time':'3 – 7 days','svc.oto.price':'From €900',
    'svc.mento.name':'Mentoplasty','svc.mento.desc':'Chin implant or reduction to balance facial features and enhance the profile. Perfect harmony with the nose and cheekbones.','svc.mento.time':'5 – 10 days','svc.mento.price':'From €1,400',
