    'svc.abdo.name':'Abdominoplasty','svc.abdo.desc':'Removal of excess abdominal skin and muscle tightening for a flat, toned stomach. Ideal after pregnancy or significant weight loss.','svc.abdo.time':'14 – 21 days','svc.abdo.price':'From €2,500',
