    'svc.arm.name':'Arm Lift','svc.arm.desc':'Brachioplasty to eliminate excess arm skin after weight loss or with age. Firm, toned arms restored.','svc.arm.time':'7 – 14 days','svc.arm.price':'From €1,800',
    'svc.thigh.name':'Thigh Lift','svc.thigh.desc':'Cruroplasty to firm and reshape the inner thighs after weight loss. Restore firm, harmonious thighs.','svc.thigh.time':'10 – 21 days','svc.thigh.price':'From €2,200',
